  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Angle wide open

          -  Age &gt; 65 yrs

          -  IOP &gt; 23 and &lt; 30 mmHg (average of the two highest readings of the daily IOP phasing)

          -  Topical beta blocker in fellow eye

          -  At least two medications in use + previous ALT

          -  MD &lt; 20 dB (HFA 24-2 full threshold)

          -  LOCSII &lt; C1-N1-P0
